Full Description: KAPUA was founded to enable companies to make better demand and financial planning decisions by radically improving planning and forecasting accuracy and speed. This increased accuracy allows organizations to lower working capital while improving fulfillment levels.   Related research in this field suggests a 3M profit increase on a 100M business driven by a 10-20% improvement of forecasting accuracy, and KAPUA set out to take this even further. In multiple cases, we're able to reduce a company's forecasting error to a 10th of what it was before. As AI is taking over a lot of the manual work, planners can now focus on developing new strategies to maximize revenue and minimize working capital.   Because AI is able to detect patterns in your internal and external data sets, our implementation approach becomes really low-touch and therefore extremely accelerated: we can set up a tenant in our public or private SaaS environment within a few weeks from start to finish. Full Description: The WTN is a curated membership community comprised of the world's most innovative individuals and organizations in science, technology, and related fields. The WTN brings key players together – from cutting-edge technologists to forward-thinking financiers, from conceptual futurists to grounded entrepreneurs, from insightful science writers to savvy marketers, from big-picture government officials to focused policy analysts, and from the world's leading corporations to the world's newest start-ups – helping to make things happen sooner and better than they might have. The WTN exists to encourage serendipity – the happy accidents of colliding ideas and new relationships that cause the biggest breakthroughs for individuals and institutions. Full Description: The Triea System delivers heat without using fossil fuels and at significant savings over propane, natural gas, and oil-fired heating equipment. The Triea System serves commercial buildings of all types, the agricultural industry and deployable needs, such as for military and emergency preparedness functions. The Triea System is an innovative heat exchange system that lets you transfer heat from existing sources rather than burning fossil fuels. Those heat sources include chiller waste heat, solar heat, and heat from composting animal manure and other available sources. Transferring this “free” rejected heat provides significant savings in operating costs and real sustainability. Triea Systems have been used successfully on poultry farms, in commercial warehouses, self-storage facilities and many other applications. Triea Systems even has mobile systems for remote locations.

Live In Peace has become a second family to many young people in East Palo Alto and eastern Menlo Park.
